<h1 id="article-heading_1-0" class="comp article-heading mntl-text-block">
How to Reset a PS4 Controller</h1><!-- end: comp article-heading mntl-text-block -->
<h2 id="article-subheading_1-0" class="comp article-subheading">
A soft reset corrects a variety of memory and software issues; a hard reset erases everything</h2><!-- end: comp article-subheading -->
<div id="article-meta_1-0" class="comp article-meta mntl-block" data-tracking-container="true">
<div id="tech-bylines_1-0" class="comp tech-bylines mntl-bylines">
<div id="mntl-bylines__group_1-0" class="comp mntl-bylines__group--author mntl-bylines__group mntl-block">
<div id="mntl-bylines__item_1-0" class="comp mntl-bylines__item mntl-attribution__item mntl-attribution__item--has-date">
<span class="mntl-attribution__item-descriptor">By</span>
<div data-tooltip="Daniel Nations has been a tech journalist since 1994. His work has appeared in Computer Currents, The Examiner, and other publications. He is a developer who has published apps in the Apple App Store, Google Play marketplace and Amazon Appstore; he also has worked as a data analyst and DB administrator." data-inline-tooltip="true">
<a
href="https://www.lifewire.com/daniel-nations-1993996"
rel="nocaes"
data-trigger-link="true"
class="mntl-attribution__item-name"
>Daniel Nations</a><!-- end: mntl-attribution__item-name -->
