</figure><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-universal-image figure-landscape figure-high-res -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-40" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-42" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-43" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Now that we&#39;ve forgotten the malfunctioning DualShock 4 controller, we want to power down the PS4. You can do this by holding down the PS4 button on your controller, navigating to <strong>Power</strong> in the menu and choosing <strong>Turn off PS4</strong>.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-44" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-46" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-47" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Connect your misbehaving DualShock 4 controller to the PS4 using a USB cable.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-48" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-50" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-51" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Turn on the PS4 and wait for it to boot up.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-52" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-54" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-55" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Press the <strong>PlayStation </strong>button on the controller and login to the PS4. The PlayStation 4 controller should now be paired and you can test to see if it&#39;s still misbehaving.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-56" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
</OL>
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-how-to-hard-reset-a-ps4-controller"></span> <h2 id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-59" class="comp mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> How to Hard Reset a PS4 Controller </span> </h2><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading -->
<figure id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-60" class="comp mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-universal-image figure-landscape figure-high-res">
<div class="figure-media">
<div class="img-placeholder" style="padding-bottom:66.6%;">
<img
data-src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/DR5y1HM8NB1lJdG9R8-K2VSbPhI=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/how-to-reset-ps4-controller-4174025-3cf04986aa0e4c3f99a54264ffed7199.png"
width="3000"
height="2000"
alt="Person resetting a PlayStation 4 controller with a paperclip"
class="lazyload universal-image__image"
data-expand="300"
data-hi-res-src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/IisqYSUndWsqDn3X-7I2jNATQuA=/2000x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/how-to-reset-ps4-controller-4174025-3cf04986aa0e4c3f99a54264ffed7199.png"
id=mntl-sc-block-image_1-0-6
data-click-tracked="true"
data-tracking-container="true"
data-img-lightbox="true"
/>
<noscript>
<img
src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/DR5y1HM8NB1lJdG9R8-K2VSbPhI=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/how-to-reset-ps4-controller-4174025-3cf04986aa0e4c3f99a54264ffed7199.png"
width="3000"
height="2000"
class="img--noscript universal-image__image"
