/>
</noscript>
</div>
</div>
<figcaption id="mntl-figure-caption_1-0" class="comp mntl-figure-caption figure-article-caption">
<span class="figure-article-caption-owner"><p>Lifewire / Miguel Co</p></span>
</figcaption><!-- end: comp mntl-figure-caption figure-article-caption -->
</figure><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-universal-image figure-landscape figure-high-res -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-61" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
A hard reset is when a device is reverted back to its factory default settings, which is basically how it came out of the box.If a soft reset fails and you&#39;re still having troubles, this process can frequently resolve any problems.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-62" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-63" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Thankfully, this is easy to do with the DualShock 4 controller, but you&#39;ll need a paper clip or something similar to reset your PS4 controller.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-64" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-65" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Follow these steps to perform a hard reset on your controller:
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-66" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<OL id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-67" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--OL mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--OL mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-68" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-69" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Power down the PS4.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-70" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-72" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-73" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Turn over the DualShock 4 controller and locate the small hole near the left shoulder button.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<figure id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-74" class="comp mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-universal-image figure-landscape figure-high-res">
<div class="figure-media">
<div class="img-placeholder" style="padding-bottom:66.6%;">
<img
data-src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/cxUUEFJ993s7r_DCKjvMaUlazT4=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/008-how-to-reset-ps4-controller-4174025-11d7a57ac2154500a9f3e504135daac5.jpg"
width="1500"
height="1000"
alt="A DualShock 4 controller with the reset hole highlighted"
class="lazyload universal-image__image"
data-expand="300"
data-hi-res-src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/cxUUEFJ993s7r_DCKjvMaUlazT4=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/008-how-to-reset-ps4-controller-4174025-11d7a57ac2154500a9f3e504135daac5.jpg"
id=mntl-sc-block-image_1-0-7
data-click-tracked="true"
data-tracking-container="true"
data-img-lightbox="true"
/>
<noscript>
<img
src="https://www.lifewire.com/thmb/cxUUEFJ993s7r_DCKjvMaUlazT4=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/008-how-to-reset-ps4-controller-4174025-11d7a57ac2154500a9f3e504135daac5.jpg"
width="1500"
height="1000"
class="img--noscript universal-image__image"
alt="A DualShock 4 controller with the reset hole highlighted"
/>
</noscript>
</div>
</div>
</figure><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-universal-image figure-landscape figure-high-res -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-75" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-77" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-78" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Unfold one end of the paper clip and insert it to push the button buried inside the hole.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-79" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-81" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-82" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Hold down this button for about 5 seconds.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-83" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-85" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-86" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Connect the controller to the PS4 using a USB cable.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-87" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-89" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-90" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Turn on the PS4 and wait for it to boot up.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-91" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
<LI id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-93" class="comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup"><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-group--LI mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-startgroup -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-94" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
Press the <strong>PlayStation </strong>button on the controller to log into the PS4.The light bar should turn blue indicating the DualShock 4 has paired with the console.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-95" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
</LI>
</OL>
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-98" class="comp theme-experttipnote mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-callout mntl-sc-block-callout mntl-block" data-tracking-id="mntl-sc-block-callout" data-tracking-container="true">
<div id="mntl-sc-block-callout-body_1-0-2" class="comp mntl-sc-block-callout-body mntl-text-block">
<p>These instructions may not work for a modded PS4 controller. If you have trouble following the directions, consult the manufacturer of your controller.</p></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-callout-body mntl-text-block -->
</div><!-- end: comp theme-experttipnote mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-callout mntl-sc-block-callout mntl-block -->
