data-tracking-id="featured-link"
><span class="link__wrapper">Why Is My PS4 Controller Blinking Blue, White, Red, or Orange?</span>
<svg class="icon icon-arrow-right ">
<use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-arrow-right"></use>
</svg></a><!-- end: mntl-sc-block-featuredlink__link mntl-text-link -->
</div><!-- end: comp related-link mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-block -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-100" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-still-having-problems-with-your-ps4-controller"></span> <h2 id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-101" class="comp mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading"> <span class="mntl-sc-block-heading__text"> Still Having Problems With Your PS4 Controller? </span> </h2><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-heading mntl-sc-block-heading -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-102" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
If you are still having problems with your controller, try <a href="https://www.lifewire.com/how-to-properly-restart-a-router-modem-2624570" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">restarting your router or modem</a>. Remember, you'll lose Internet access, so warn anyone in the house before doing this step.&nbsp;&nbsp;
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-103" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<p id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-104" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html">
If you were unable to sync your PS4 controller, run through the steps for doing a hard reset <em>with the router or modem turned off</em>.&nbsp;If you did pair your device but it is still erratic, try using it with the router and modem off. If that works, you need to <a href="https://www.lifewire.com/wifi-channel-number-change-to-avoid-interference-818208" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">change the Wi-Fi channel on your router</a>.
</p><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-105" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-106" class="comp featured-link mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-block">
<a
href="https://www.lifewire.com/best-playstation-4-games-4045233"
rel="nocaes"
