><span class="link__wrapper">The 10 Best PlayStation 4 Games to Buy in 2022</span>
<svg class="icon icon-arrow-right ">
<use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-arrow-right"></use>
</svg></a><!-- end: mntl-sc-block-featuredlink__link mntl-text-link -->
</div><!-- end: comp featured-link mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-block -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-107" class="comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block"></div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block -->
<div id="mntl-sc-block_1-0-108" class="comp theme-expanded mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-faq mntl-sc-block-faq mntl-block">
<span class="heading-toc" id="toc-frequently-asked-questions-3aa667ab-8fa1-46c5-8472-335f12d53c08"></span>
<div id="mntl-sc-block-faq__title_1-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block-faq__title mntl-text-block">
FAQ</div><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-faq__title mntl-text-block -->
<ul id="mntl-sc-block-faq__content_1-0" class="comp mntl-sc-block-faq__content mntl-accordion">
<li class="accordion__item js-accordion-item is-active">
<div class="accordion__header js-accordion-trigger" id="mntl-sc-block-faq__content_1-section-0">
<span class="accordion__title">How do you sync a PS4 controller?</span>
</div><!--end accordion__header-->
<div class="accordion__body">
<div id="mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content_1-0-section-0" class="comp class com.about.mantle.model.extended.docv2.sc.blocks.StructuredContentFaqEx$Faq mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content">
<div class="faq-accordion__item-answer">
<p>To <a href="https://www.lifewire.com/how-to-sync-ps4-controller-4173785" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">sync a PS4 controller</a>, start by plugging it into the console. Turn on the PS4 and press the controllers <strong>PS</strong> button. You can then wirelessly add additional controllers using the consoles Bluetooth settings.</p>
</div>
</div><!-- end: comp class com.about.mantle.model.extended.docv2.sc.blocks.StructuredContentFaqEx$Faq mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content -->
</div><!--end accordion__body-->
</li><!--end accordion__item-->
<li class="accordion__item js-accordion-item is-active">
<div class="accordion__header js-accordion-trigger" id="mntl-sc-block-faq__content_1-section-1">
<span class="accordion__title">How do you fix PS4 controller drift?</span>
</div><!--end accordion__header-->
<div class="accordion__body">
<div id="mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content_1-0-section-1" class="comp class com.about.mantle.model.extended.docv2.sc.blocks.StructuredContentFaqEx$Faq mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content">
<div class="faq-accordion__item-answer">
<p>To <a href="https://www.lifewire.com/fix-ps4-controller-drift-5093965" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">fix drift</a>, ensure your controller is turned off. Try a soft reset, and a hard reset if that doesnt work. You can also clean your controller or replace its analog sticks.</p>
</div>
</div><!-- end: comp class com.about.mantle.model.extended.docv2.sc.blocks.StructuredContentFaqEx$Faq mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content -->
</div><!--end accordion__body-->
</li><!--end accordion__item-->
<li class="accordion__item js-accordion-item is-active">
<div class="accordion__header js-accordion-trigger" id="mntl-sc-block-faq__content_1-section-2">
<span class="accordion__title">Why won&#39;t my PS4 controller charge?</span>
</div><!--end accordion__header-->
<div class="accordion__body">
<div id="mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content_1-0-section-2" class="comp class com.about.mantle.model.extended.docv2.sc.blocks.StructuredContentFaqEx$Faq mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content">
<div class="faq-accordion__item-answer">
<p>If <a href="https://www.lifewire.com/fix-ps4-controller-that-wont-charge-5076360" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="internalLink" data-ordinal="1">your controller wont charge</a>, it could be an issue with the charging port or cable, a problem with the PS4 that prevents it from providing power over USB, or an issue with the controllers battery.</p>
</div>
</div><!-- end: comp class com.about.mantle.model.extended.docv2.sc.blocks.StructuredContentFaqEx$Faq mntl-sc-block-faq__accordion-content -->
</div><!--end accordion__body-->
</li><!--end accordion__item-->
</ul><!-- end: comp mntl-sc-block-faq__content mntl-accordion -->
<!--end accordion -->
</div><!-- end: comp theme-expanded mntl-sc-block tech-sc-block-faq mntl-sc-block-faq mntl-block -->
</div><!-- end: comp structured-content expert-content mntl-sc-page mntl-block -->
